<h3 class="text-gray-1100 text-24 mb-4px">Scott Stewart, PhD</h3>
<div class="font-sans text-14">Clinical Professor at Cornell Universitys Samuel Curtis Johnson Graduate School of Management, Cornell SC Johnson College of Business</div>
</div>
</div>
<svg class="collapsed-icon w-24px h-24px ml-4px" viewBox="0 0 320 512">
